@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_meuxfr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(v2 + 0.75)) / 0.57)
    v0 = 0.45
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.52) - (v1 + 0.97 / tmp + 0.70)) / wp.sin(v0))
    tmp = 0.30
    data[tid] = v0
